profile:
ResQ is a Canadian registered pest control company owned and operated by experienced exterminators dedicated to providing safe, effective and speedy results. 

For many years ResQ Canada has proudly been the go to company for the most difficult pest problems. Working with government, Multi-family dwelling, Industrial, Commercial & Residential. 

Some of the pest we deal with most frequently are: Racoons, Possums, Skunks, Squirrels, Mice, Rats, Birds, Bedbugs, Cockroaches, Ants, Flies, Wasp & Bees. 

ResQ strictly follows Pest control practices and procedures under the given guidelines of Ministry of Environment (MOE), Ministry of Health & their appropriate regulations and strictly follows the principles of Integrated Pest Management (IPM) techniques.

ResQ offers high quality professional Pest Control Treatment and Training (T&T) to its Household and Commercial clients at a very affordable prices.

ResQ sends its technicians in the ministry approved UNMARKED vehicles without a company logo on it to protect the household privacy.
services: Elimination and preventative solutions for Rodents, Wildlife, Birds, Bedbugs, Cockroaches, Wasp, Ants and many more crawling or flying pest. Free home inspections and education available with no obligation. Contact us to speak with one of our Pro's who will be more then happy to assist you with all of your needs and questions.
warranty_terms: Yes. Contact us for more info.
